---
// arquivo: src/components/About.astro
---

<section class="about-section">
	<div class="container about-grid stagger-in">
		<div class="visual">
			<div class="image-wrapper">
				<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542744173-8e7e53415bb0?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600" alt="Processo de trabalho" />
				<div class="asterisk-overlay">*</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="content">
			<h2>Trabalhamos de <span class="text-outline">Forma Inteligente</span>, Um Esforço que Conta.</h2>
			<p>
				Deixe-nos guiar seu negócio até o topo do mercado digital. 
				Avaliamos, planejamos e executamos com precisão metodológica para garantir o sucesso.
			</p>

			<div class="progress-bars">
				<div class="bar-item">
					<div class="bar-header">
						<span>Design de Web</span>
						<span>90%</span>
					</div>
					<div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 90%"></div></div>
				</div>
				<div class="bar-item">
					<div class="bar-header">
						<span>Estratégia SEO</span>
						<span>85%</span>
					</div>
					<div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 85%"></div></div>
				</div>
				<div class="bar-item">
					<div class="bar-header">
						<span>Marketing Digital</span>
						<span>95%</span>
					</div>
					<div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 95%"></div></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about-section {
		padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
	}
	.about-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
		gap: 80px;
		align-items: center;
	}
	.image-wrapper {
		position: relative;
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.image-wrapper img {
		width: 100%;
		aspect-ratio: 4/3;
		object-fit: cover;
		filter: grayscale(100%);
		transition: 0.5s;
	}
	.image-wrapper:hover img {
		filter: grayscale(0%);
	}
	.asterisk-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 20px;
		right: 20px;
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 80px;
		line-height: 0.5;
		color: var(--color-primary);
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 64px);
		margin-bottom: 24px;
	}
	p {
		margin-bottom: 40px;
	}
	.bar-item {
		margin-bottom: 24px;
	}
	.bar-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-weight: 600;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		margin-bottom: 8px;
	}
	.bar-bg {
		height: 4px;
		background: var(--color-border);
		width: 100%;
		border-radius: 4px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.bar-fill {
		height: 100%;
		background: var(--color-primary);
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
		.image-wrapper img { aspect-ratio: 16/9; }
	}
</style>
